      "body" : "I think those 3 downvotes are because you say &quot;there is no default&quot; which is a fairly unclear statement. As you say, an uninitialized object reference points to <code>null</code>. <code>null</code> is the default, so I&#39;m not sure what you are referring to when you say there isn&#39;t one. (Did you maybe mean something like &quot;<code>Boolean</code> is neither <code>true</code> nor <code>false</code> by default&quot;?)"
