    "last_edit_date" : 1530653188,
    "creation_date" : 1307099270,
    "answer_id" : 6226314,
    "question_id" : 6226290,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>An uninitialized <code>Boolean</code> member (actually a reference to an object of type <code>Boolean</code>) will have the default value of <code>null</code>.</p>\n\n<p>An uninitialized <code>boolean</code> (primitive) member will have the default value of <code>false</code>.</p>\n"
  }, {
