    "body" : "<p>The default value for a <code>Boolean</code> (object) is <code>null</code>.<br />\nThe <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/java/nutsandbolts/datatypes.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">default value</a> for a <code>boolean</code> (primitive) is <code>false</code>.</p>\n"
